1.0.name: wordpress/nano-blogger
1.0.description: nano blogger is a search engine optimized blog framework for WordPress. It supports custom header, custom background, 2 custom menu, two sidebar widget area, and unlimited plugins. It has two different template for both Pages and Blogs, so you can call seperate blog page into any of your site page. Gorgeous and soothing look is ideal for blog and even for your website.
